title: Rochard dominant for No. 2 Virginia Tech in shutout victory against Boston College - VT hokiesports.com
content: Rochard dominant for No. 2 Virginia Tech in shutout victory against Boston College  VT hokiesports.com
description: BRIGHTON, MASS -- Senior Keely Rochard was dealing on Friday, throwing a four-hit shutout to lead the No. 2 Virginia Tech Hokies over the Boston College Eagles 3-0.
